{"tid":185640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中文大學國際生舍堂女子上吊亡","createTime":"2017-04-03T15:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T15:35:26.000Z","uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9852be9e680aeca1889e5308883ec915c6b1cfc8","tid":185640,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T15:12:27.000Z","msg":"【22:50】警方更正地點為國際生舍堂<br />\n<br />\n晚上9時許，沙田中文大學有職員報案，指國際生舍堂內有一名女子上吊。消防接報到場，將女子解下，經救護員檢驗證實她已氣絕身亡。警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"a5b5563e81cac3af8fe8b617e741b3b5eff271bd","tid":185640,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T15:13:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68b2c12270578f60fa4504362d25ce71cef81be7","tid":185640,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T15:26:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>福氣來架👍，一諗到係香港死做爛做買唔到一層300呎樓，一份人工養唔起冚家😅，喂！福氣來架👍<br />\n<br />\n港喱廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/31/171138_0e38f2989bcff71aeeb92a8d6399e905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F31%2F171138_0e38f2989bcff71aeeb92a8d6399e905.jpg&h=2755b6fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我鄉下隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/583ti0i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F583ti0i.jpg&h=c69a313e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港喱廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/31/171251_77c7faf61f75ca10c19c36b8f89bdf96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F31%2F1712